{"an10.79:0.1":"Anguttara Nikaya 10.79 ","an10.79:0.2":"8. Akankhavagga ","an10.79:0.3":"Aghatavatthusutta ","an10.79:1.1":"“Dasayimani, bhikkhave, aghatavatthuni. ","an10.79:1.2":"Katamani dasa? ","an10.79:1.3":"‘Anattham me acari’ti aghatam bandhati; ","an10.79:1.4":"‘anattham me carati’ti aghatam bandhati; ","an10.79:1.5":"‘anattham me carissati’ti aghatam bandhati; ","an10.79:1.6":"‘piyassa me manapassa anattham acari’ti …pe… ","an10.79:1.7":"‘anattham carati’ti …pe… ","an10.79:1.8":"‘anattham carissati’ti aghatam bandhati, ","an10.79:1.9":"‘appiyassa me amanapassa attham acari’ti …pe… ","an10.79:1.10":"‘attham carati’ti …pe… ","an10.79:1.11":"‘attham carissati’ti aghatam bandhati; ","an10.79:1.12":"atthane ca kuppati—","an10.79:1.13":"imani kho, bhikkhave, dasa aghatavatthuni”ti. ","an10.79:1.14":"Navamam. "}